/* ÔöÇÔöÇ Root ÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇ */
export default function Dashboard() {
  const nav = useNavigate();
  const { profile, balance } = useOutletContext() || {};

  const [tournaments, setTournaments] = useState([]);
  const [messages,    setMessages]    = useState([]);
  const [stats,       setStats]       = useState({
    played: 0, wins: 0, kills: 0, winRate: 0,
    rank: null, total_points: 0, top3: 0,
  });
  const [daily,    setDaily]    = useState(null);
  const [liveData, setLiveData] = useState({ liveCount: 0, onlineCount: 0, lastWinner: null });
  const [missions, setMissions] = useState([]);
  const [loading,  setLoading]  = useState(true);

  const coins    = balance ?? 0;
  const role     = ROLES[profile?.role?.toLowerCase()] ?? ROLES.user;
  const division = getDivision(stats.rank);

  /* ÔöÇÔöÇ Data load ÔöÇÔöÇ */
  const load = useCallback(async () => {
    if (!profile?.id) return;

    const [
      { data: trn },
      { data: st },
      { data: msgs },
      { data: claims },
      { data: lastResult },
      { data: onlineProfiles },
      { data: activeMatches },
    ] = await Promise.all([
      supabase.from("tournaments")
        .select("id,name,status,max_players,current_players,prize_coins,entry_fee,mode,start_date")
        .in("status", ["open", "in_progress"])
        .order("created_at", { ascending: false })
        .limit(6),
      supabase.from("player_stats").select("*").eq("user_id", profile.id).maybeSingle(),
      supabase.from("admin_messages").select("*").order("created_at", { ascending: false }).limit(3),
      supabase.from("user_daily_claims").select("*").eq("user_id", profile.id).order("claimed_at", { ascending: false }).limit(7),
      supabase.from("match_results")
        .select("user_id, points, profiles!match_results_user_id_fkey(full_name)")
        .eq("status", "verified").eq("placement", 1)
        .order("submitted_at", { ascending: false }).limit(1),
      supabase.from("profiles").select("id").gte("last_seen", new Date(Date.now() - 5 * 60 * 1000).toISOString()),
      supabase.from("tournaments").select("id").eq("status", "in_progress"),
    ]);

    setTournaments(trn ?? []);
    setMessages(msgs ?? []);

    if (st) {
      setStats({
        played: st.tournaments_played ?? 0,
        wins:   st.wins ?? 0,
        kills:  st.kills ?? 0,
        rank:   st.rank ?? null,
        total_points: st.total_points ?? 0,
        top3:   st.top3_finishes ?? 0,
        winRate: st.wins > 0 && st.tournaments_played > 0
          ? Math.round((st.wins / st.tournaments_played) * 100)
          : 0,
      });
    }

    const liveCount   = (activeMatches ?? []).length;
    const onlineCount = (onlineProfiles ?? []).length;
    const lastWinner  = lastResult?.[0]
      ? { name: lastResult[0].profiles?.full_name || "Joueur", points: lastResult[0].points }
      : null;
    setLiveData({ liveCount, onlineCount, lastWinner });

    const todayClaim = (claims ?? []).find(c =>
      new Date(c.claimed_at).toDateString() === new Date().toDateString()
    );
    setDaily({ canClaim: !todayClaim, streak: claims?.length ?? 0 });

    // Build missions from stats
    if (st) {
      const m = [];
      if (st.tournaments_played === 0)
        m.push({ icon: "­ƒÄ«", text: "Joue ton 1er tournoi", prog: 0, target: 1, done: false });
      else if (st.wins === 0)
        m.push({ icon: "­ƒÅå", text: "Gagne ton 1er tournoi", prog: 0, target: 1, done: false });
      else
        m.push({ icon: "­ƒÅå", text: "Victoires", prog: st.wins, target: Math.max(5, st.wins + 3), done: false });

      m.push({ icon: "­ƒÄ»", text: "Kills", prog: st.kills, target: Math.max(10, st.kills + 5), done: false });

      if (!todayClaim)
        m.push({ icon: "­ƒÄü", text: "Bonus quotidien", prog: 0, target: 1, done: false });
      else
        m.push({ icon: "­ƒÄü", text: "Bonus r├®clam├®", prog: 1, target: 1, done: true });

      setMissions(m.slice(0, 3));
    }

    setLoading(false);
  }, [profile?.id]);

  /* ÔöÇÔöÇ Effects ÔöÇÔöÇ */
  useEffect(() => {
    if (!profile?.id) return;
    load();

    const ch = supabase
      .channel(`hub-${profile.id}`)
      .on("postgres_changes", { event: "*", schema: "public", table: "tournaments" }, p => {
        if (p.eventType === "INSERT" && ["open", "in_progress"].includes(p.new.status))
          setTournaments(prev => [p.new, ...prev].slice(0, 6));
        else if (p.eventType === "UPDATE")
          setTournaments(prev =>
            prev.map(t => t.id === p.new.id ? p.new : t)
              .filter(t => ["open", "in_progress"].includes(t.status))
          );
      })
      .on("postgres_changes", {
        event: "UPDATE", schema: "public", table: "player_stats",
        filter: `user_id=eq.${profile.id}`,
      }, p => {
        const s = p.new;
        setStats({
          played: s.tournaments_played ?? 0,
          wins:   s.wins ?? 0,
          kills:  s.kills ?? 0,
          rank:   s.rank ?? null,
          total_points: s.total_points ?? 0,
          top3:   s.top3_finishes ?? 0,
          winRate: s.wins > 0 && s.tournaments_played > 0
            ? Math.round((s.wins / s.tournaments_played) * 100)
            : 0,
        });
      })
      .subscribe();

    return () => supabase.removeChannel(ch);
  }, [profile?.id, load]);

  const nextTournoi  = tournaments.find(t => t.status === "open" && t.start_date);
  const countdownNext = useCountdown(nextTournoi?.start_date);

  if (loading) return <LoadingScreen />;

  return (
    <div className="db-page">
      {/* Welcome */}
      <WelcomeSection
        profile={profile}
        stats={stats}
        balance={coins}
        division={division}
        role={role}
      />

      {/* Live banner ÔÇö only if something is active */}
      <LiveBanner liveData={liveData} countdownNext={countdownNext} />

      {/* Stats row */}
      <StatsRow stats={stats} />

      {/* Main 2-col grid */}
      <div className="db-main-grid">
        {/* Left: tournaments */}
        <TournamentsSection tournaments={tournaments} />

        {/* Right: rank + missions + daily */}
        <div className="db-side-stack">
          <RankCard stats={stats} division={division} />
          <MissionsPanel missions={missions} />
          <DailyPanel daily={daily} />
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Quick actions */}
      <QuickActions profile={profile} />

      {/* Announcements */}
      <AnnouncementsPanel messages={messages} />

      {/* Sticky mobile CTA */}
      <div className="db-sticky-cta">
        <Button
          variant="primary"
          size="lg"
          className="ui-btn-full"
          onClick={() => nav("/tournaments")}
        >
          Rejoindre un tournoi
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}

